al;\">&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<ol style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-inline-start: 48px;\" start=\"2\">\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: 3.299999999999997pt; padding-left: 18pt;\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.295; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Gouvernance &amp; Organigramme&nbsp;: l&rsquo;utilisateur de ce document doit chercher un lien entre ces deux termes c&rsquo;est-&agrave;-dire v&eacute;rifier si la gouvernance est d&eacute;finie de mani&egrave;re coh&eacute;rente par rapport &agrave; l&rsquo;organigramme de l&rsquo;entit&eacute;. Obtenir&nbsp; l&rsquo;organigramme formel de l&rsquo;entreprise, les personnes qui la gouvernent, leurs CV, etc&hellip;.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<ol style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-inline-start: 48px;\" start=\"3\">\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: 3.299999999999997pt; padding-left: 18pt;\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.295; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">D&eacute;finitions de fonctions (r&ocirc;les et responsabilit&eacute;s)&nbsp;: v&eacute;rifiez si des responsabilit&eacute;s sont li&eacute;es &agrave; chaque poste et si les postes ou les fonctions sont dot&eacute;s de cahiers de charges ou de fiches de postes, s&rsquo;il y a eu des &eacute;changes sur ces fiches avec le personnel, etc...</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<ol style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-inline-start: 48px;\" start=\"4\">\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: 3.299999999999997pt; padding-left: 18pt;\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.295; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Gestion de la client&egrave;le&nbsp;: &agrave; travers la prise de connaissance g&eacute;n&eacute;rale du client, on devra &ecirc;tre en mesure de donner tous les risques qui tournent autour de la gestion de la client&egrave;le de l&rsquo;entreprise&nbsp;: les proc&eacute;dures de vente et de r&egrave;glements des clients dans l&rsquo;entreprise. Recenser les principaux clients de l&rsquo;entreprise, les monnaies et les langues dans lesquelles les factures sont &eacute;mises, les litiges connues ou en cours etc&hellip;</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<ol style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-inline-start: 48px;\" start=\"5\">\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: 3.299999999999997pt; padding-left: 18pt;\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.295; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Gestion de la tr&eacute;sorerie&nbsp;: identifier les risques li&eacute;s &agrave; la gestion de la tr&eacute;sorerie par exemple, risque de taux de change, absence de budget, inexactitude li&eacute;e aux entr&eacute;es et sorties, existence des comptes bancaires et recenser lesdits comptes, les signataires, le d&eacute;tenteur des ch&eacute;quiers, la gestion de la caisse, l&rsquo;existence des PV d&rsquo;inventaires de caisse, l&rsquo;existence des titres de placements, les d&eacute;couverts obtenus, etc&hellip;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<ol style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-inline-start: 48px;\" start=\"6\">\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: 3.299999999999997pt; padding-left: 18pt;\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.295; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Gestion des autres actifs&nbsp;: il faut demander aux clients les immobilisations qu&rsquo;ils d&eacute;tiennent (incorporelles, corporelles et financi&egrave;res), la codification des immobilisations, l&rsquo;organisation et la gestion des stocks, les magasins, la gestion juridique des produits p&eacute;rim&eacute;s, d&eacute;t&eacute;rior&eacute;s aux fins de constitution des d&eacute;pr&eacute;ciations, etc&hellip;</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<ol style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-inline-start: 48px;\" start=\"7\">\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: 3.299999999999997pt; padding-left: 18pt;\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.295; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Gestion des fournisseurs&nbsp;: recenser les principaux fournisseurs avec qui le client traite et identifier les risques qui sous-tendent les relations entre ses fournisseurs et lui demander comment il r&egrave;gle ses fournisseurs, la monnaie et la langue dans lesquelles les factures sont &eacute;mises, les litiges connues ou en cours, etc&hellip;.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<ol style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-inline-start: 48px;\" start=\"8\">\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: 3.299999999999997pt; padding-left: 18pt;\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.295; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Gestion des autres passifs&nbsp;: il s&rsquo;agira ici de v&eacute;rifier l&rsquo;ad&eacute;quation entre les capitaux propres de l&rsquo;entreprise et les risques pr&eacute;visibles, le niveau des capitaux propres par rapport au capital social, les lib&eacute;rations selon le droit des soci&eacute;t&eacute;s, etc&hellip;.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<ol style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-inline-start: 48px;\" start=\"9\">\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: 3.299999999999997pt; padding-left: 18pt;\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.295; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Historique fiscal et social du client&nbsp;: faire le point des imp&ocirc;ts auxquels le client est soumis&nbsp;; prendre aussi connaissance des redressements fiscaux et sociaux majeurs subis par lui et en d&eacute;terminer les diff&eacute;rentes causes principales et les risques li&eacute;s. V&eacute;rifier si le personnel est d&eacute;clar&eacute; &agrave; la CNSS, si l&rsquo;entreprise b&eacute;n&eacute;ficie des all&egrave;gements fiscaux li&eacute;s aux sp&eacute;cificit&eacute;s de son secteur d&rsquo;activit&eacute; et &eacute;galement au regard des premiers emplois cr&eacute;&eacute;s (Non-paiement VPS pendant 2 ans, b&eacute;n&eacute;fice de cr&eacute;dit d&rsquo;imp&ocirc;ts), etc&hellip;.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<ol style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-inline-start: 48px;\" start=\"10\">\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: 3.299999999999997pt; padding-left: 18pt;\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.295; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Organisation comptable&nbsp;: identifier le logiciel comptable utilis&eacute;, le plan de compte du client ainsi que les principaux sch&eacute;mas d&rsquo;&eacute;critures qu&rsquo;engendrent les op&eacute;rations sp&eacute;cifiques et transactions effectu&eacute;es par le client, etc&hellip;.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong style=\"font-weight: normal;\"><br /><br /></strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.295; margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">II- Documentation</span></p>\r\n<p><strong style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<ol style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-inline-start: 48px;\">\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt; padding-left: 18pt;\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.295; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Lois &amp; R&egrave;glements&nbsp;: Prendre connaissance du r&eacute;f&eacute;rentiel comptable applicable &agrave; l&rsquo;entit&eacute; (AUDCIF, CIMA, PCB &hellip;) et autres textes sp&eacute;cifiques qui r&egrave;glementent le secteur d&rsquo;activit&eacute;s du client. Il faut prendre copie de ces documents, les lire et tirer les conclusions et en garder copie dans son Dossier Permanent.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<ol style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-inline-start: 48px;\" start=\"2\">\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt; padding-left: 18pt;\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.295; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Proc&eacute;dures&nbsp;: v&eacute;rifier l&rsquo;existence d&rsquo;un manuel de proc&eacute;dures, si oui, est-il appliqu&eacute;&nbsp;? Si non, mettre en place un syst&egrave;me pour son &eacute;laboration et s&rsquo;assurer qu&rsquo;il existe un guide de comptabilisation. S&rsquo;il n&rsquo;existe pas de manuel de proc&eacute;dures, en proposer au client et </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">le facturer</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong style=\"font-weight: normal;\"><br /><br /></strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.295; margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">III- Syst&egrave;me d&rsquo;information</span></p>\r\n<p><strong style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<ol style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-inline-start: 48px;\">\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: 3.299999999999997pt; padding-left: 18pt;\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.295; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Mat&eacute;riel informatique&nbsp;: identifier les mat&eacute;riels informatiques utilis&eacute;s par le client et voir s&rsquo;ils sont en ad&eacute;quation avec ses activit&eacute;s, etc&hellip;.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<ol style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-inline-start: 48px;\" start=\"2\">\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: 3.299999999999997pt; padding-left: 18pt;\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.295; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Logiciel Informatique utilis&eacute;&nbsp;: identifier tous les logiciels qu&rsquo;utilise le client pour la gestion de ses activit&eacute;s. Appr&eacute;cier si ces logiciels ont des licences achet&eacute;es et r&eacute;pondent aux besoins du client, etc&hellip;.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<ol style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-inline-start: 48px;\" start=\"3\">\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: 3.299999999999997pt; padding-left: 18pt;\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.295; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 8pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">S&eacute;curit&eacute; informatique&nbsp;: v&eacute;rifier si les outils informatiques sont bien s&eacute;curis&eacute;s, hors sinistre &eacute;lectrique, intrusion informatique, s&rsquo;il y a une assurance souscrite pour couvrir les sinistres sur les mat&eacute;riels, s&rsquo;il y a de disques durs externes pour la sauvegarde des donn&eacute;es de l&rsquo;entreprise, etc&hellip;.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.295; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 8pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Total des fr&eacute;quences&nbsp;:</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.295; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 8pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">La fr&eacute;quence est d&eacute;termin&eacute;e en faisant le total des cases coch&eacute;es par niveau.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.295; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 8pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Pour l&rsquo;exemple ci-dessous&nbsp;; on obtient les fr&eacute;quences ci-apr&egrave;s&nbsp;:&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><strong style=\"font-weight: normal;\"><br /><br /></strong></p>\r\n<div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-left: 0pt;\" align=\"left\">\r\n<table style=\"border: none; border-collapse: collapse;\"><colgroup><col width=\"113\" /><col width=\"246\" /><col width=\"104\" /><col width=\"104\" /><col width=\"104\" /></colgroup>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr style=\"height: 1pt;\">\r\n<td style=\"vertical-align: middle; background-color: #bdd7ee; padding: 0pt 3.5pt 0pt 3.5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word; border: solid #000000 0.5pt;\" rowspan=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001; text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Processus</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"vertical-align: middle; background-color: #bdd7ee; padding: 0pt 3.5pt 0pt 3.5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word; border: solid #000000 0.5pt;\" rowspan=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001; text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Sous processus</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"vertical-align: middle; background-color: #bdd7ee; padding: 0pt 3.5pt 0pt 3.5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word; border: solid #000000 0.5pt;\" colspan=\"3\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001; text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Niveau de risques</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"height: 1pt;\">\r\n<td style=\"vertical-align: middle; background-color: #bdd7ee; padding: 0pt 3.5pt 0pt 3.5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word; border: solid #000000 0.5pt;\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001; text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Faible</spa